parameters.text:
=Your task: Create 1 image prompt and {{ $('Get Sheet Inputs').item.json.scenes }}  video prompts as guided by your system guidelines. Scene 0 will be the image prompt, and Scenes 1 onward will be the video prompts. 

Make sure that the reference product image is depicted as ACCURATELY as possible in the resulting images, especially all text.

***


Character description: {{ $('Get Sheet Inputs').item.json.character_description }}

Setting description: {{ $('Get Sheet Inputs').item.json.setting_description }}

Voice description: {{ $('Get Sheet Inputs').item.json.voice_description }}

Script description: {{ $('Get Sheet Inputs').item.json.script_description }}

Other requests: {{ $('Get Sheet Inputs').item.json.other_requests }}

Aspect ratio: {{ $('Get Sheet Inputs').item.json.aspect_ratio }}


***
Description of the reference images are given below. Most likely these are descriptions of a character advertising the product, or the product to be advertised itself. 

{{ $('Analyze Image').item.json.choices[0].message.content }}


***
Use the Think tool to double check your output. Especially to check that the number of image prompts you generated align to the requested number above.

